        }
      },
      "webhookId": "fdce7c4d-3f61-47de-83fb-bd519094fb3a"
    },
    {
      "id": "f89ce719-6bac-485d-b44b-0c8bbbe40b72",
      "name": "Sticky Note f89ce719",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        576,
        384
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Multi-Stage AI Workflow (IDE UX -> CLI UX)\n\n**Flow:** Form intake -> Stage 1 IDE Analyzer -> Stage 2 CLI Generator -> Split Files -> Commit to GitHub\n\n- **Stage 1 (IDE-style AI):** analyses the task + existing code and emits a structured integration plan (JSON).\n- **Stage 2 (CLI-style AI):** consumes that plan and produces runnable script files + a commit message.\n- **Integration:** each file is committed to the target GitHub repo, removing manual copy/paste.\n\n**Adaptability:** the model sub-nodes are swappable (OpenAI/Gemini/Anthropic) without changing the chain topology.",
        "width": 520,
        "height": 320
      }
    }
  ],
